criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  male or female subjects, between 18 and 55 years old (inclusive);

          -  body mass index (BMI) of 27-40 kg/m2;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  likely allergy or sensitivity to any components of Trodusquemine for Injection based
             on known allergies to drugs of the same class, or which, in the opinion of the
             Principal Investigator, suggests an increased potential for an adverse
             hypersensitivity to trodusquemine HCl;

          -  any subject with a history of allergy (rash, hives, breathing difficulty, etc.) to any
             medications, either prescription or nonprescription, including dietary supplements or
             herbal medications;

          -  any subject with a history of severe allergy or bronchial asthma;
